rComments: He's a really good prof and cares so much about each of his students. He will know your name by the third class. Lots of papers and group projects but they're chill and fun!

This prof was amazing, if you want an easy elective take this class with this prof. He gives 100% on all assignments. Also, the midterm and final are open book and super easy. Recommend if you want an easy class.

This is a horrible teacher! He is not clear whatsoever and he is extremely boring. His lectures are very long, all he does is read the slides word per word and never adds any comments after reading them. The things we learned in class did not go with the course at all. We never even opened the textbook either. I don't recommend this class to anyone
